{"tid":1778681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際專家組決定請辭 推到林鄭出來交代","createTime":"2019-12-11T06:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T07:03:19.000Z","uid":241000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb20ca0b85abd6faf605bf3bab9869ac0fb95fe5","tid":1778681,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:34:38.000Z","msg":"事件因你而起<br />\n<br />\n受罪嘅點解要係一班愛香港嘅香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要用黑警來鎮壓香港人<br />\n<br />\n我可以放棄香港<br />\n<br />\n但你一定要放曬所有因為你嘅獨裁暴政 而被拉嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱經緯扑人一下要坐監 班暴徒扑人扑到頭破血流 開槍當打機 點解可以消遙法外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你口中香港嘅法治去咗邊<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查委員會成立得未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f8e91f4f531a2b5c1d3b5dfdb3fc788a0e387","tid":1778681,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美加議員講對華政策，<br />\n響task2 急要人</span></span><br />\n適逢人權日，世界上人權被打壓嘅國家或地區唔少，當然其中一個亮點係打壓緊香港同新疆嘅中國！<br />\n<br />\n多國政要發推文關注中國打壓人權嘅情況，精選推文遍布task 1 &amp; 2，大家快啲去回應啦！<br />\n<br />\n記得落hashtag #humanrights #HumanRightsDay 呀～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwn8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=1f2887fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"c8073d25359ce6291c28d789c8563e15e8e18fc6","tid":1778681,"uid":230298,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"